This is the Syfou's X Utils site regeneration infrastructure. It needs:

- GNU Make (tested on gnu make 3.81)
- find (tested on GNU find 4.3.0)
- htmltidy (tested on htmltidy 5.10.26)
- sed (tested on GNU sed 4.1.5)
- python (tested on python 2.5.0)
- asciidoc (tested on asciidoc 8.1.0)
- source-highlight (tested on source-highlight 1.11)

Just type:

make...............Build the whole site in place
make prepare.......Copy the site tree under tmp/
make publish.......Rsync the file to berlios (with proper credentials)
make clean.........Clean everything

